From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: OpenAI <noreply@openai.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 16:55:00 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] winex11: define libX11 soname for Android builds.

Android/Termux X11 packages may not expose a SONAME through Wine's
configure probes even though libX11 is available.  Keep winex11.drv
buildable by using the runtime library name directly.
---
 dlls/winex11.drv/x11drv_main.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/dlls/winex11.drv/x11drv_main.c b/dlls/winex11.drv/x11drv_main.c
index 2b1757bb..55d1c3b2 100644
--- a/dlls/winex11.drv/x11drv_main.c
+++ b/dlls/winex11.drv/x11drv_main.c
@@ -36,6 +36,10 @@
 #include <assert.h>
 #include <dlfcn.h>
 #include <X11/cursorfont.h>
 #include <X11/Xlib.h>
 #include <X11/XKBlib.h>
+#ifndef SONAME_LIBX11
+#define SONAME_LIBX11 "libX11.so"
+#endif
+
 #ifdef HAVE_X11_EXTENSIONS_XRENDER_H
 #include <X11/extensions/Xrender.h>
 #endif
-- 
